metadata.name: Medusa of Balance
metadata.description:
Striving for a more modest, comfortable and balanced existence and learning to settle for what you have, you'll throw a huge weight off your shoulders. Life will become easier for both you and others. And most importantly, you will acquire the most valuable resource in abundance - time.

In a world where people are tied to their gadgets around the clock and to-do lists have no end, there is nothing more valuable than the ability to unload, slow down and lead a less stressful life, devoting more time to your favorite activities.

My balance jellyfish will remind you of yourself loved
